{"tid":2037794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(咁都得?傳媒評論員?)警批傳媒報道偏頗 忽略中環射胡椒球因果","createTime":"2020-05-27T07:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T08:34:46.000Z","uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9f659b2448bf0d80b3429b299d8000f340dbedfd","tid":2037794,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"警方指，有傳媒在報道內文中只提及人群在中環一帶聚集，隻字不提人群堵路及投擲雜物的行為，更形容人群是沿馬路「逃跑」，批評相關報道內容非常偏頗，忽略警方使用胡椒球的前因後果。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2476441/%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%B9%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E5%81%8F%E9%A0%97+%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E5%B0%84%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E7%90%83%E5%9B%A0%E6%9E%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2476441%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%2581%258F%25E9%25A0%2597%2B%25E5%25BF%25BD%25E7%2595%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25B0%2584%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%259E%259C&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=0edae8f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2476441/%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%B9%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E5%81%8F%E9%A0%97+%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E5%B0%84%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E7%90%83%E5%9B%A0%E6%9E%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，下午1時許，中環一帶有人群佔據及堵塞馬路，包括畢打街、皇后大道中、德己立街，甚至有人在馬路上向警察投擲水樽等雜物，警方別無他法，才使用最低所需武力，包括使用胡椒球以制止相關違法及暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n此外，警方指下午約2時45分，旺角有人羣一度走出馬路，警方正在現場疏導交通，又警告人群停止非法堵路，警方會採取執法行動。"},{"pid":"7893c9577e9bb808fd9bc517f05693220549135e","tid":2037794,"uid":179775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"有曬片"},{"pid":"38432b34f1ea04cb26fc1e70369ba212924b649b","tid":2037794,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"人哋25k全港最大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi